title: Ep 200: Reflections on the 200 Show
description: Thank you so much for listening to The Psych Files  for the past 6 1/2 years.  In this episode I provide a little background on how the podcast started and what has happened as it grew over the years.  It just past 8 million downloads and I want to share a few thoughts on this with you.
